high_descs: Turn around and walk around to face the left side of the kitchen table.
Pick up the knife on the kitchen table.
Look right to face the apple on the kitchen table.
Cut the apple on the kitchen table into three pieces.
Look up to face the kitchen table.
Place the knife on the kitchen table.
Look down to face the apple on the kitchen table.
Pick up the piece of apple on the kitchen table.
Turn around and step forward to face the fridge.
Cool the piece of apple in the fridge and remove it.
Turn around to face the kitchen table.
Place the apple piece on the kitchen table.
anns.task_desc: TO cool a piece of apple and place it on the kitchen table.

high_descs: Turn right then right again and face the black table to your right.
Take the knife off of the table in front of you.
Turn right then left and face the table on your left.
Slice the apple on the table in front of you.
Look at the apple on the table in front of you.
Place the knife by the apple on the table in front of you.
Look at the apple on the table in front of you.
Take an apple slice off of the table in front of you.
Turn left and face the fridge on your left.
Place the apple slice in the fridge in front of you then take it out.
Turn left and face the table to your left.
Place the apple slice on the table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold apple slice on the table.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn right and go to the table
Pick up the knife on the table
Go around the table to the right side of the table
Cut the apple on the table
Turn to the middle of the table
Put the knife on the table
Turn to the edge of the table
Pick up an apple piece from the table
Turn left, go forward, turn left to the fridge
Put the apple piece in the fridge, wait, pick up the apple piece from the fridge
Turn left, go forward, turn left to the table
Put the apple piece on the table
anns.task_desc: Cut an apple, cool a piece of the apple
